{"id":470379612,"lang":"cpp","time":"9 months, 1 week","timestamp":1616293455,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/470379612/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Second Largest Digit in a String","memory":"7 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int secondHighest(string s) {\n        \n        vector<int> ans;\n        map<int,int> m1;\n        \n        for(char c : s){\n            if( c>='0'&& c<='9'){\n                if(m1[c] == 0)\n                    ans.push_back(c-'0');\n                m1[c] = 1;\n            }\n        }\n        sort(ans.begin(),ans.end());\n        reverse(ans.begin(),ans.end());\n        if(ans.size() <= 1){\n            return -1;\n        }\n        return ans[1];\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"second-largest-digit-in-a-string"}
